content:
for those interested in historical archive formats, we have an `ere` spec now that covers execution history _only_, from genesis to now: https://github.com/eth-clients/e2store-format-specs/pull/16 - this bridges the gap created after era1/era - there are two more specs being worked on:
* erb for blobs
* erc for consensus data _only_ (unlike era which also includes execution payloads) - these will complement `ere`
